{"tid":965422,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《怪奇物語》第三季播映時間確定","createTime":"2019-01-02T04:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T10:06:51.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbfeaaa17517a78007d076a00c628af9ffe46fdc","tid":965422,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"《怪奇物語》從 2016 年開播至今，儼然已經成為 Netflix 平台上最成功的作品之一，其有趣的世界觀、緊湊的節奏和復刻 80 年代的氛圍，精準的網羅各個族群，雖然 2018 年的萬聖節我們看不到全新一季，也深怕那些可愛的小朋友就這樣默默長大了，不過終於，《怪奇物語》第三季的播映時間隨著全新海報終於明朗！定於 2019 年美國國慶日 7 月 4 日假期，強攻院線市場！<br />\n《怪奇物語》第三季將繼續由麥特德弗（Matt Duffer）、羅斯德弗（Ross Duffer）兩兄弟打造，而演出卡司包括米莉芭比布朗（Millie Bobby Brown）、諾亞舒奈普（Noah Schnapp）、芬恩沃夫海德（Finn Wolfhard）、蓋登馬塔拉佐（Gaeten Matarazzo）、卡萊柏麥拉格林（Caleb McLaughlin）、薇諾娜芮德（Winona Ryder）、查理希頓（Charlie Heaton）、、娜塔莉亞戴爾（Natalia Dyer）、喬基瑞（Joe Keery）、莎迪辛克（Sadie Sink）等都將回歸。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g3djJ9pNJEM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg3djJ9pNJEM&d=8bpNXnFkE57gNuvy2jcr2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=1b09d6d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g3djJ9pNJEM</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hypesphere.com/files/images/Nth6kRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2FNth6kRp.jpg&h=388c9450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Fnews%2F16222&d=8bpNXnFkE57gNuvy2jcr2YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a9906129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16222</a>"},{"pid":"9d024bfed948278ace15e9276324bf5b66087a0f","tid":965422,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2feb9e4f81d0d57d82d4eee4e03729126ed753","tid":965422,"uid":128445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"沒David harbour 